com.complexible.common.protobuf.io

Class InputStreamSizeDelimitedProtobufReader<T extends com.google.protobuf.MessageLite>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.protobuf.io.InputStreamSizeDelimitedProtobufReader<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProtobufReader<T>

    public final class InputStreamSizeDelimitedProtobufReader<T extends com.google.protobuf.MessageLite>
extends Object
implements ProtobufReader<T>

    Implementation of a ProtobufReader which will read Protobuf messages from an InputStream. Assumes the messages are length delimited with a fixed-width big endian coded integer which is the size of the subsequent message.

    Since:
    1.0
